    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>butterflied chicken</strong> and cook for 4 min on each side until golden, then reduce the heat to medium</p><p>Add the <strong>zingy</strong> <strong>sauce </strong>and cook for a further 3-4 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
