    {
      "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>cooked chicken </strong>to a clean chopping board and slice – this is your <strong>zingy chicken</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> zingy chicken</strong> with the <strong>vegetable rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Pour over any <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>zingy</strong> <strong>sauce </strong>and garnish with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
